title: Grateful Dead Live at Greek Theatre, U. Of California on 1985-06-14
lineage: Master PCM > DAW (via SEKD Prodif) > Wav > cdwav > Flac
description: Dancin' In The Streets, West L.A. Fadeaway, CC Rider, Peggy-O, Hell In A Bucket, Keep On Growing-> Stagger Lee-> Let It Grow-> Deal Morning Dew-> Playin' In The Band-> China Doll-> Drums-> Truckin'-> Smokestack Lightning-> Comes A Time-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Day Job

reviews.review_text:
AMAZING GREEKS!!!!!!!! THIS SHOW ROCKS, SMOKES... dEW TO OPEN 2ND SET, CHINA DOLL AND BREAKING OUT COMES A TIME, STAGGERLEE, FIRST KEEP ON GROWING WITH PHIL AND BRENT SINGING IT TOGETHER!! AND I THOUGHT THE 84 GREEKS WERE SICK, THIS SHOW IS RIGHT THERE WITH THOSE!

EQUIPTMENT PROBLEMS DURING 1ST SET, THEY TOOK SHORT BREAK AND THEN CAME BACK AND SCORCHED KEEP ON GROWING!
A night to remember! This is a great audiance tape that really captures the evening-- my first Greek show and it was truely majical. try it you'll like it!

AUD Test Drive If you are comparing AUDs on this fantastic show, may I suggest that you test dive by playing the opening few notes of Morning Dew.    Hello Phil.  Most people greet by shaking hands.  Not Phil: 
He shakes the house.

Actually, with this recording, most people are going to be limited by their speakers, not this recording.  Just a superb AUD.
